\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33178,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/11\/faith-jihad-hajj-best-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":11895,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Deeds: Faith, Jihad, Hajj better than all other deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ma\u2019iz al-Tamimi reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was asked, \u201cWhich deeds are best?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cFaith in Allah alone, then jihad, and then a blessed pilgrimage are better than all other deeds like the distance between the rising of the sun and its setting.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33083,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/03\/no-better-time-10-days\/","url_meta":{"origin":11895,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dhul-Hijjah: No better time for good deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo good deeds can be done at a time better than these first ten days of Dhul-Hijjah.\u201d It was said, \u201cNot even jihad in the way of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cNot even jihad in the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32265,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyha